{"id":21949,"date":"2024-01-18T17:13:29","date_gmt":"2021-05-18T11:43:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=21949"},"modified":"2022-05-31T11:39:28","modified_gmt":"2022-05-31T06:09:28","slug":"gaming-room-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/gaming-room-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Cool Gaming Room Interior Design Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Spruce up your entertainment game with these seven gaming room ideas for your home<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As the lines blur between a proper workplace and home, as well as outdoor and entertainment spaces, there is a dire need to create an environment that helps your home become an all-encompassing sanctuary. While a gaming room or a gaming corner is much appreciated in an office environment, you can create one at home too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A gaming room can be for people of all ages. As adults, most of whom are juggling our entire lives from home, it is necessary to create a space that gives you some respite. With children at home 24&#215;7, it is equally necessary to give them props that keep them engaged and not constantly on their screens. What better than creating a fun gaming room or a gaming corner that helps everybody unwind? Take a look at these seven gaming room design inspirations for your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Your Own Pool Table For A Fun Gaming Room Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>So what if you cannot head out for the weekend? A pool table in your house can make up for those missed night outs! If you are aiming to create a proper bar atmosphere at home, some of the aspects that you need to think of apart from the pool table itself are:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Lighting<\/li><li>Seating options<\/li><li>Flooring<\/li><li>Wall colours<\/li><li>A bar\/snack counter<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Tip: A gaming room design for a pool table should ideally draw inspiration from subtly lit bars.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162821\/pool-table-best-gaming-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"Pool table gaming room designed in grey colour with classic lights and table looks vintage.\" class=\"wp-image-21958\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162821\/pool-table-best-gaming-room-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162821\/pool-table-best-gaming-room-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162821\/pool-table-best-gaming-room-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162821\/pool-table-best-gaming-room-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Miss heading out with your friends? Get a pool table for some in-house unwinding<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Proper Gaming Room Design Is A Must For An Online Gaming Enthusiast<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As a gamer, you would possibly be juggling many lives together apart from your own! A proper corner, or even better a proper gaming room design, is a must to have you play in peace. We absolutely love this slick dark corner that is perfect for your tech set-up. The dark colours also create the right ambience and provide privacy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162750\/computer-gaming-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"Computer gaming room design in white colour with ambient lighting and wooden table lends a sleek look.\" class=\"wp-image-21954\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162750\/computer-gaming-room-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162750\/computer-gaming-room-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162750\/computer-gaming-room-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162750\/computer-gaming-room-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>You need a cool gaming station for that eat-sleep-play-and-repeat routine<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Game For A Workout?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Keeping yourself fit is a part of the game too, right? We know how many of you miss going out for your regular workouts. Well, you can set up a home gym too. Not your typical gaming room design idea, a gym can still provide you with that much-needed break for rejuvenation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162744\/combine-fitness-with-fun-gaming-room-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Gaming room interior design, small gym room combined with fun is a part of the game too.\" class=\"wp-image-21953\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162744\/combine-fitness-with-fun-gaming-room-interior-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162744\/combine-fitness-with-fun-gaming-room-interior-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162744\/combine-fitness-with-fun-gaming-room-interior-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162744\/combine-fitness-with-fun-gaming-room-interior-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Combine fitness with fun with a dedicated gym room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Related Article <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/home-gym-ideas\/\">Home Gym Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Are You In For Board Game Nights?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019ll be honest: We prefer playing board games in the real world no matter how convenient apps can get. Set your home up for fun board game nights. You\u2019ll require a minimal set-up \u2014 primarily a proper table and seating arrangements \u2014 to create the right ambience. For two-person games like chess, for example, a cosy nook in your house would be the best place for a set-up. Throw in a comfortable rug and cushions, and you are all set!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162829\/small-gaming-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"Small gaming room design, cosy nook place with a proper table and seating for fun board game night best set up.\" class=\"wp-image-21959\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162829\/small-gaming-room-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162829\/small-gaming-room-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162829\/small-gaming-room-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162829\/small-gaming-room-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Small gaming room design can cater to creating a dedicated corner for a board game night<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gaming Room Design For The Mind Games<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If games equal rummy, poker, mahjong and the works for you, you can opt for the best gaming room design for your home. Wooden finishes for the essential furniture like the table and chairs, side stools and benches for non-playing guests can create a wonderful ambience. Classic touches like a chandelier and upholstered furniture can add a unique charm in such a game room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162811\/indoor-games-room-design-for-mind-gamers.jpg\" alt=\"An indoor game room designed with a card table and chairs in a wooden finish create a beautiful ambience.\" class=\"wp-image-21957\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162811\/indoor-games-room-design-for-mind-gamers.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162811\/indoor-games-room-design-for-mind-gamers-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162811\/indoor-games-room-design-for-mind-gamers-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162811\/indoor-games-room-design-for-mind-gamers-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>We\u2019re laying the design cards on the table with this one<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Back To Childhood<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Need a corner to unwind but do not want to invest too much in it? You can think of simpler options for a gaming room design at home. Sometimes, simple additions can get you exactly what you need. A swing ticks all the right boxes \u2014 takes you back to some rather carefree times, is for all ages and can come in tons of options to fit into your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162737\/childhood-gaming-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"Gaming room design with swing brings back childhood memories.\" class=\"wp-image-21952\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162737\/childhood-gaming-room-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162737\/childhood-gaming-room-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162737\/childhood-gaming-room-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162737\/childhood-gaming-room-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>re there any grown-ups that claim to have outgrown the swing?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Gaming Room Design To Keep The Young Ones Busy<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The toughest ones to please and keep entertained for longer attention spans, your kids definitely need a gaming room as much as you do. A cool set-up for your children to engage with their toys is a good investment. You can add fun, outdoorsy elements like a wall-climbing set-up to ensure that your child gets some physical exercise too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162757\/design-your-dream-room-game-for-young-ones.jpg\" alt=\"Design your dream room game; Kids room has a wall-climbing set-up that keeps entertained for longer attention spans.\" class=\"wp-image-21955\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162757\/design-your-dream-room-game-for-young-ones.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162757\/design-your-dream-room-game-for-young-ones-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162757\/design-your-dream-room-game-for-young-ones-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/18162757\/design-your-dream-room-game-for-young-ones-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Design a special playing space for the kids to keep them entertained<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It\u2019s all fun and games till you cannot practically step out for entertainment. A gaming room in your house can be a great way to relieve stress in the post-pandemic world. Change the game and get yourself a dedicated entertainment space that takes you on simple immersive experiences minus the phone or laptop screens!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, more about<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/game-room-decor-ideas\/\">Game Room Decor Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/kids-playroom-ideas\/\">Kids Playroom Ideas<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-l